---
title: Caribbean Beef Strips & Couscous with Veggies, Charred Corn & Lemon Mayo
description: The couscous is so fluffy that it’s cuddling beef strips in a warm hug. Let those flavours embrace you with
Caribbean jerk seasoning and veggies, with a zap from the zesty mayo drizzled over at the end.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
